{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-10-2",
 "title": "Nature Girl Sees Through the Disguise",
 "summary": "Wandering down into the staging area of the swoop arena, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie -- in his scarred, green-haired Mege Vauki persona -- crosses paths with the limping Colonel Altair Quila, fresh off her crash aboard the Achernar, and the diplomat Eva Sargent. Bazil politely praises Altair's racing and introduces himself as a stranger from Team KIF, but as he turns to leave, Altair recognizes his voice and nearly blurts out \"Baz,\" hastily disguising it as a cough. Bazil deftly plays along, dropping veiled hints and a discreet finger-to-lips signal for silence to protect his cover, which the perceptive Sargent notices without prying. The three exchange cordial farewells, agreeing to meet again at the awards ceremony, before Bazil slips off toward the public stables to avoid lingering in public.",
